{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-dang-001__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-dang-001", "source_id": "daya-dang-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·蕩之什·001.1", "text_original": "蕩蕩上帝，下民之辟。疾威上帝，其命多辟。\n天生烝民，其命匪諶。靡不有初，鮮克有終。", "text_normalized": "蕩蕩上帝，下民之辟。疾威上帝，其命多辟。\n天生烝民，其命匪諶。靡不有初，鮮克有終。", "notes": "蕩 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-dang-001__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-dang-001", "source_id": "daya-dang-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·蕩之什·001.2", "text_original": "文王曰咨！咨女殷商，曾是彊禦，曾是掊克。\n曾是在位，曾是在服。天降滔德，女興是力。", "text_normalized": "文王曰咨！咨女殷商，曾是彊禦，曾是掊克。\n曾是在位，曾是在服。天降滔德，女興是力。", "notes": "蕩 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-dang-001__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-dang-001", "source_id": "daya-dang-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·蕩之什·001.3", "text_original": "文王曰咨！咨女殷商，而秉義類，彊禦多懟。\n流言以對，寇攘式內。侯作侯祝，靡屆靡究。", "text_normalized": "文王曰咨！咨女殷商，而秉義類，彊禦多懟。\n流言以對，寇攘式內。侯作侯祝，靡屆靡究。", "notes": "蕩 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-dang-001__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-dang-001", "source_id": "daya-dang-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·蕩之什·001.4", "text_original": "文王曰咨！咨女殷商，女炰烋于中國，斂怨以為德。\n不明爾德，時無背無側。爾德不明，以無陪無卿。", "text_normalized": "文王曰咨！咨女殷商，女炰烋于中國，斂怨以為德。\n不明爾德，時無背無側。爾德不明，以無陪無卿。", "notes": "蕩 Chinese stanza 4."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-dang-001__005__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-dang-001", "source_id": "daya-dang-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·蕩之什·001.5", "text_original": "文王曰咨！咨女殷商，天不湎爾以酒，不義從式。\n既愆爾止，靡明靡晦；式號式呼，俾晝作夜。", "text_normalized": "文王曰咨！咨女殷商，天不湎爾以酒，不義從式。\n既愆爾止，靡明靡晦；式號式呼，俾晝作夜。", "notes": "蕩 Chinese stanza 5."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-dang-001__006__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-dang-001", "source_id": "daya-dang-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·蕩之什·001.6", "text_original": "文王曰咨！咨女殷商，如蜩如螗，如沸如羹。\n小大近喪，人尚乎由行。內奰于中國，覃及鬼方。", "text_normalized": "文王曰咨！咨女殷商，如蜩如螗，如沸如羹。\n小大近喪，人尚乎由行。內奰于中國，覃及鬼方。", "notes": "蕩 Chinese stanza 6."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-dang-001__007__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-dang-001", "source_id": "daya-dang-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·蕩之什·001.7", "text_original": "文王曰咨！咨女殷商，匪上帝不時，殷不用舊。\n雖無老成人，尚有典刑。曾是莫聽，大命以傾。", "text_normalized": "文王曰咨！咨女殷商，匪上帝不時，殷不用舊。\n雖無老成人，尚有典刑。曾是莫聽，大命以傾。", "notes": "蕩 Chinese stanza 7."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-dang-001__008__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-dang-001", "source_id": "daya-dang-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 8, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·蕩之什·001.8", "text_original": "文王曰咨！咨女殷商，人亦有言，顛沛之揭。\n枝葉未有害，本實先撥。殷鑒不遠，在夏后之世。", "text_normalized": "文王曰咨！咨女殷商，人亦有言，顛沛之揭。\n枝葉未有害，本實先撥。殷鑒不遠，在夏后之世。", "notes": "蕩 Chinese stanza 8."}
